1.4.1	If you use Acronis, you use their True Image product.	St
1.4.2	Disk Director deals mostly with partitioning.	St
1.4.3	You could use Acronis True Image to create a full backup image of your existing drive but you'd want to be sure that the restoration process would go smoothly.	St
1.4.4	You'd be moving to RAID-0 which means Windows needs the RAID drivers that go with your motherboard.	St
